    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo taws Kalps atsibst to/ jo es efinu grehkojs/tomehr rau- gi/ es efinu schodeen nahzis tas pirmajs no wiﬀa Jahsepa Nam- ma/ mannam Kungam tam Keh- ninam pretti-eedans.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad atbildeja Abisajus Zerujas Dehls/ un fazzija: Ne bij tad Simejum par to noḱau- tam tapt/ ka wiꞥſch ta KUN- GA Swaiditu irr lahdejs?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Dahwids: Kas man ar jums jadarra juhs Zerujas Dehli/ ka juhs man scho- deen gribbat par Prettineeku tapt? bij schodeen jebkahdam no- kautam tapt eekch Israëta? woj es tad ne finnu/ ka es schodeen par Kehninu tappis efinu pahr Israëlu?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Kehniisch fazzija us Simeju: Tew ne buhs nomirt. Un tas Kehniisch swehreja tam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir Mewibosets/ Saula Dehls nonahze tam Kehninam pretti. Un wiꞥſch ne bij fawas Kahjas nedś fawu Bahrdn schihstijś/ nedś fawas Drehbes masgajs no tahś Deenas/ kad tas Kehniisch bij nogahjts/ lihds tai Deenai/ kad tas Kehniisch atkat ar Meern atnahze.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad wiꞥſch Jerusale- mê tam Kehninam pretti nahze/ tad fazzija tas Kehniisch us to: Kapehz ne efftu ar mannim nah- zie/ Mewiboscts?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Unwiꞥſch fazzija: Man Kungs Kehniisch/ mans Kalp irr manni peewihlis/ jo tan Kalps fazzija: Es liſschu few we nu Eyseli fedloht/ un jahschu u to/ un eefchu pee ta Kehnitza/ j taws Kalps irr tiflis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Unwiꞥſch irr arridfan ta wn Kalpu pee manna Kunga t Kehnina apsuhoſejs. Bet man Kungs tas Kehniisch irr ka ween Deewa Engelis/ darri/ kas te labbi patiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo wiﬀs manna Tehu Nams irr zitts ne ka bijis/ k ween Nahwes Faudis preekf manna Kunga ta Kehniin Tatschu tu effi tawn Kalpu sta teem lizzis/ kas pee taru Bald ehd/ kahda Tatsniba man ta wehl irr/ jeb par ko man wai us to Kehniinu jabrehz?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas Kehniis us to: Kapehz tu wairak run no tatwahm Veetahm? es efir fazzijs : Tu un Zihbus dalla to Tihrunnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mewibosets fazzija to Kehnizu: Lai wiꞥſch arridfa wiﬀu nemm/ pehz to/ ka man Kungs tas Kehniisch attat Meeru taru Namna nahzis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Barsillajus tas G leaditeris nahze arridfan no Ro lim/ un gabje ar to Kehnizu pa to Jardanu/ ka wiꞥſch to pa to Jardanu pawadditu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Barsillajus bija fo ti wezz/ pee aftendefinitis Ga deem/ un bij to Kehnizu ustn reje\n"
    }
  ],
